   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns_235_ms_f_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
               مرید حضرت
               <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جهان</persName>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>, disciple of Lord
                  <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName></mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبده الاقران    
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
               چودهری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
               قانونگوی پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               بعنایت
               <lb/>امیدوار بوده بدانند عرضه داشتی که درینولا مشتملبر حقیقت
               <lb/>باقی سنه
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۱۰۶۵</num></date>
               و از رسیدن کس وزارت پناه 
               <persName ref="#kifayatKhan">کفایتخان</persName>
               <lb/>ارسالداشته بودند بنظر در آمد باید که آنچه باقی حسابی باشد
               <lb/>واصل سازند و در هر باب که سخن داشته باشند به
               <lb/>وزارت پناه مذکور بنویسند و موافق جواب عملنمایند
               <lb/>درین باب تاکید دانسته بموجبی که نوشته شد
               <lb/>بعمل آورند و از فرموده تخلف و انحراف نورزند
               <lb/>تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۷</num>
               شهر شعبان سنه
               <num>۱۰۶۹</num></date>
               هجری
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>,
               <lb/>having hoped for kindness, know that at this time, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> containing
               the facts
               <lb/>of the arrears of the year
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1065</date><note>This is equivalent to 1654–55 in the Gregorian calendar.</note>
                and the arrival of a [deputed] person of the Refuge of Ministry
               <persName ref="#kifayatKhan">Kifayat Khan</persName>
               <lb/>that had been sent has come to the attention [of <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>]. It is necessary that whatever arrears shall be calculated
               <lb/>should be collected. If [<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>] have anything to say about any matter,
               <lb/>write to the said Refuge of Ministry [<persName ref="#kifayatKhan">Kifayat Khan</persName>], and act according to [his] response.
               <lb/>Knowing this to be settled according to that which is written,
               <lb/>execute it. And do not oppose what has been ordered.
               <lb/>Written on the
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">7th
                of the month of Shaban in the year
                <num>1069</num>
               </date>
               Hijri. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور مقرر شناسند
               <lb/>اگر سخن حسابی باشد ظاهر سازند شرافت پناه
               <lb/>قاضی جیو نیز در انجا تشریف دارند
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
             </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p>
               <lb/>Know it to be settled as written.
               <lb/>If there is anything to say [about] the accounting, make it known; Refuge of
               Goodness
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">Qazi</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref> will also go there. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing
               further</g>.</p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_f_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>
               پروانه نواب مستطاب 
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازشخان</persName>
               <gap/>
               جیو
               <lb rend="empty"/><unclear>بنابر</unclear>
               جواب
               <unclear>بقایا</unclear>
               <gap/>
               سنه
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۱۰۶۵</num></date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6">
            <p>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nawab">Nawab</ref>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>
               [Qazi] <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>.
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <unclear>Because of</unclear> the response to <unclear>the arrears of</unclear> <gap/> the year <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>1065</num></date>.
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
